				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\lambda $$\end{document} is the wavelength of the incident light [98]). Considering the solar light spectrum [104], the latter behaviour makes particle in the dimensional range 0.1 μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
