				\begin{document}$$\lambda $$\end{document} = 654 nm and 405 nm (red and blue lines, respectively). Note the two positions of the split time individuated at each wavelength (dotted circles) which differ for more than 30 s: EC determined @ λ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
